data.name: OLE2Shape
desc: This service is for an OLE shape.

properties.name: CLSID
desc: If you get this property you get the CLSID of the OLE2 document stream contained in this OLE2 shape.
If you set it, an empty OLE2 document stream with this CLSID is created within this OLE2 shape.

properties.name: IsInternal
desc: This property returns TRUE for all OLE2 that are internal Office components.

properties.name: Model
desc: This is the model for the OLE2 inside this shape.
This property returns an empty reference if the OLE2 is not an Office component.

properties.name: PersistName
desc: this is the internal storage name that keeps this OLE2 persist.
